description: Keep up to date with the latest slang in this Urban Dictionary app. Browse the over 5 million definitions on urbandictionary.com. Features include Search, Word of the Day, Random, and Sharing via Email, Text Message, or simply Copying to the Clipboard. This app serves as a handy guide to the definitions of the latest in urban culture. Browsing the entries with the Random feature will provide much entertainment! Notice: The content in this app is user submitted and may not be appropriate for users under the age of 18. Notice: This app is in no way endorsed, recommended, recognized,  or affiliated with urbandictionary.com
